# AMR-GigaWord 200k

# ::id 0 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok first-time appearances by clint black , leann rimes and michael w. smith at the florida strawberry festival highlight the event 's #### lineup in march .
# ::alignments
(h / highlight-01
      :ARG0 (a / appear-01
            :ARG1 (a2 / and
                  :op1 (p / person
                        :name (n / name
                              :op1 "Clint"
                              :op2 "Black"))
                  :op2 (p2 / person
                        :name (n2 / name
                              :op1 "Leann"
                              :op2 "Rimes"))
                  :op3 (p3 / person
                        :name (n3 / name
                              :op1 "Michael"
                              :op2 "W."
                              :op3 "Smail")))
            :time (f / festival
                  :name (n4 / name
                        :op1 "Florida"
                        :op2 " strawberry"
                        :op3 "Festival"))
            :ord (o / ordinal-entity
                  :value 1))
      :ARG1 (l / lineup
            :poss f
            :mod (t / thing
                  :name (n5 / name
                        :op1 "###")))
      :time (m / march-01))

# ::id 1 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok australia should quickly lift restrictions on the export and enrichment of uranium , a government report found tuesday .
# ::alignments
(f / find-01
      :ARG0 (r / report
            :source (g / government-organization
                  :ARG0-of (g2 / govern-01)))
      :ARG1 (r2 / recommend-01
            :ARG1 (l / lift-01
                  :ARG0 (c / country
                        :name (n / name
                              :op1 "Australia"))
                  :ARG1 (r3 / restrict-01
                        :ARG1 (a / and
                              :op1 (e / export-01
                                    :ARG1 (u / uranium))
                              :op2 (e2 / enrich-01
                                    :ARG1 u)))
                  :ARG1-of (q / quick-02)))
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (t / tuesday)))

# ::id 2 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok minister of public security jia chunwang met here friday with tsang yam-pui , the newly-appointed commissioner of the hong kong police force of hong kong special administrative region -lrb- sar -rrb- government .

                              :op2 "Security"))
                  :ARG2 (m2 / minister)))
      :ARG1 (p2 / person
            :name (n3 / name
                  :op1 " tsang"
                  :op2 "Yam-pui")
            :ARG0-of (h2 / have-org-role-91
                  :ARG1 (f / force
                        :mod (p3 / police)
                        :mod (c / city
                              :name (n4 / name
                                    :op1 "Hong"
                                    :op2 "Kong"))
                        :part-of (g2 / government-organization
                              :name (n5 / name
                                    :op1 "Hong"
                                    :op2 "Kong"
                                    :op3 "Special"
                                    :op4 "Administrative"
                                    :op5 "Region")))
                  :ARG2 (c2 / commissioner)
                  :ARG1-of (a / appoint-01
                        :ARG1-of (n6 / new-01))))
      :location (h3 / here)
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (f2 / friday)))

# ::id 3 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok with attention focused on the launch of euro cash , the european central bank left its key interest rate unchanged thursday for the dozen countries using the new currency .
# ::alignments
(l / leave-13
      :ARG0 (b / bank
            :mod (c / central)
            :mod (c2 / continent
                  :name (n / name
                        :op1 "Europe")))
      :ARG1 (r / rate
            :mod (ii / interest)
            :ARG1-of (k / key-02)
            :poss b)
      :ARG2 (c3 / change-01
            :polarity -
            :ARG1 r
            :beneficiary (c4 / country
                  :quant 12
                  :ARG0-of (u / use-01
                        :ARG1 (c5 / currency
                              :ARG1-of (n2 / new-01)))))
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (t / thursday))
      :manner (a / attend-02
            :ARG1 (l2 / launch-01
                  :ARG1 (c6 / cash
                        :mod (e / euro)))))

                                          :ARG3 (m / most))))))

                        :name (n2 / name
                              :op1 "Michael"
                              :op2 "Jackson"))

                        :mod (ii2 / international)
                        :mod (j / jazz)
                        :location (c / city
                              :name (n3 / name
                                    :op1 "Montreal"))))
            :time (d / date-entity
                  :weekday (t2 / tuesday))))

# ::id 5 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok the nation 's community banks could play a key role in spurring an economic recovery , federal reserve chairman ben bernanke said friday , as he encouraged them to make loans so long as they can do so prudently and `` not to let fear drive '' their decisions .
# ::alignments
(s / say-01
      :ARG0 (p / person
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Ben"
                  :op2 "Bernanke")
            :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                  :ARG1 (r / reserve-01
                        :mod (f / federal))
                  :ARG2 (c / chairman)))
      :ARG1 (p2 / possible-01
            :ARG1 (p3 / play-02
                  :ARG0 (b / bank
                        :mod (c2 / community)
                        :poss (n2 / nation))
                  :ARG1 (r2 / role
                        :ARG1-of (k / key-02)
                        :ARG0-of (s2 / spur-01
                              :ARG1 (r3 / recover-01
                                    :ARG1 (e / economy))))))
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (f2 / friday))
      :time (e2 / encourage-01
            :ARG0 p
            :ARG1 b
            :ARG2 (l / loan-01
                  :ARG0 b
                  :condition (p4 / possible-01
                        :manner (p5 / prudence))
                  :ARG1-of p4
                  :manner (l2 / let-01
                        :polarity -
                        :ARG0 b
                        :ARG1 (d2 / drive-02
                              :ARG0 (f3 / fear-01)
                              :ARG1 (t / thing
                                    :ARG1-of (d3 / decide-01
                                          :ARG0 b)))))))

                                          :ARG1 (h3 / human))))))))

# ::id 7 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred

                              :name (n2 / name
                                    :op1 "India")))))
      :ARG1 (b / bust-02
            :ARG0 p
            :ARG1 (g / gang
                  :ARG0-of (l / lure-01
                        :ARG1 (p2 / person)
                        :ARG2 (d / donate-01
                              :ARG0 p2
                              :ARG1 (b2 / blood)))
                  :ARG0-of (e / extract-01
                        :ARG1 (p3 / plasma)
                        :ARG2 (b3 / blood
                              :poss p2)
                        :time (t / then))))
      :time (d2 / date-entity
            :weekday (f / friday)))

# ::id 8 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok prices on taipei 's stock futures market were higher wednesday as the taiwan stock exchange -lrb- taiex -rrb- capitalization weighted index for may moved up ## points to close at #,### , with ##,### contracts changing hands .
# ::alignments
(h / have-degree-91
      :ARG1 (t / thing
            :ARG2-of (p / price-01
                  :ARG1 (m / market
                        :mod (f / futures
                              :mod (s / stock))
                        :poss (c / city
                              :name (n / name
                                    :op1 "Taipei")))))
      :ARG2 (h2 / high-02
            :ARG1 t)
      :ARG3 (m2 / more)
      :time (w / wednesday)
      :ARG1-of (c2 / cause-01
            :ARG0 (p2 / possible-01
                  :ARG1 (m3 / move-01
                        :ARG1 (ii / index
                              :ARG2-of (w2 / weight-01
                                    :ARG1 (c3 / capitalize-01
                                          :ARG1 (s2 / stock)))
                              :mod (c4 / country
                                    :name n
                                    :op1 "Taiwan")))
                  :ARG2 (u / up-02
                        :ARG1 ii
                        :ARG2 (p3 / point))
                  :purpose (c5 / close-06
                        :ARG1 ii
                        :ARG2 p3)))
      :ARG1-of c2
      :ARG0 (c6 / change-hands-06
            :ARG1 (c7 / contract-02
                  :mod t)))

                  :op1 1000))

                  :value 1))
      :time (d2 / date-entity

      :time (a / after
            :op1 (c / criticize-01
                  :ARG0 (a2 / and
                        :op1 (j / journalist
                              :mod (p3 / prominent))
                        :op2 (m2 / minister
                              :mod (p4 / prime))

                                    :op1 "Silvio"

                              :ARG0-of (h2 / have-org-role-91
                                    :ARG2 m2))))
            :ARG1 p))

# ::alignments
(m / miss-02
      :ARG0 (p / person
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Zlatan"
                  :op2 "Ibrahimovic")
            :ARG0-of (s / strike-02)
            :poss (t / team
                  :name (n2 / name
                        :op1 "Barcelona")))
      :ARG1 (m2 / match
            :mod (c / copa
                  :mod (d / del))
            :poss (p2 / person
                  :ARG0-of (l / lead-02
                        :ARG1 (t2 / team
                              :name (n3 / name
                                    :op1 "Spanish")))))
      :time (w / week
            :mod (t3 / this))
      :time (a / after
            :op1 (ii / injure-01
                  :ARG0 p
                  :ARG1 (m3 / muscle
                        :mod (t4 / thigh))
                  :time (w2 / win-01
                        :ARG0 t
                        :ARG1 (t5 / team
                              :name (n4 / name
                                    :op1 "Mallorca"))
                        :time (d2 / date-entity
                              :weekday (s2 / saturday))))))

# ::alignments
(c / cause-01
      :ARG0 (s / strike-02
            :duration (t / temporal-quantity
                  :quant 1
                  :unit (h / hour))
            :purpose (p / protest-01
                  :ARG1 (p2 / plan-01
                        :ARG0 (g / government-organization
                              :ARG0-of (g2 / govern-01))
                        :ARG1 (a / austerity)))
            :ARG0-of p)
      :ARG1 (d / disrupt-01
            :time (d2 / date-entity
                  :weekday (t2 / thursday))
            :ARG1-of (s2 / spread-02
                  :ARG1-of (w / wide-02))
            :location (a2 / across
                  :op1 (c2 / country
                        :name (n / name
                              :op1 "France")))
            :ARG0-of (c3 / cause-01
                  :ARG1 (h2 / hit-01
                        :ARG1 (a3 / and
                              :op1 (s3 / service
                                    :mod (t3 / transport-01))
                              :op2 (s4 / school))
                        :ARG1-of (h3 / hard-02
                              :degree (p3 / particular))))))
